{"tid":1728290,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[3d print]3M 3311K 加p100/p95","createTime":"2019-11-16T20:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T20:08:58.000Z","uid":325386,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"397df1fe9f843d487797bbcb9271d05bd4557b8f","tid":1728290,"uid":325386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T20:28:03.000Z","msg":"對於放唔放呢個 design 出嚟 我係有所保留 呢隻3M 3311K防具作用有限 我唔想畀錯覺佢好撚有用， 但見到各地都有好多呢啲3M 3311K存貨......同埋有朋友對佢同情有獨鍾.....<br />\n<ins>用呢個design<strong>唔好3311k +6092x </strong>否則 濾罐過重 跑起嚟好唔舒服</ins><br />\n同埋應該檢查是否可以暢順地呼吸<br />\nP.S. plz use 6006 or 60926 if possible <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4sjLBuF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4sjLBuF.png&h=4cd9f20f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpQZFWk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpQZFWk.png&h=fc645a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K4fOzgm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4fOzgm.png&h=f13a9ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可加一塊海綿 正常3-2mm 可壓縮到 1mm(-0.5mm) 增加氣密程度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TOiHDOs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTOiHDOs.jpg&h=9c31e78c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n----3d print setting----------<br />\n<ins><strong>請使用PLA(ABS, PET 有可能對你個p100濾罐扣帶來損耗</strong></ins><br />\nlay height: 0.2mm<br />\nbrim:yes<br />\nraft: no<br />\nsupport: support enforcer ONLY<br />\n綠色位置或需要support<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMkOzia.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMkOzia.jpg&h=9af1bf98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nthis side<strong><ins> NO NEED</ins></strong> support<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqFZFYb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqFZFYb.png&h=8b7ffcc9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n---file-----<br />\nstl:<br />\n<a